---
title: Sriracha Turkey Burgers with Roasted Sweet Potatoes and Spring Mix
description: It's no secret that we're obsessed with sriracha in the HelloFresh kitchen. It's the perfect all-purpose hot sauce! We especially love it mixed with mayo and spread over this fresh ginger, garlic and shallot infused turkey burger.
